source.name: Federal Item Identification Guide (FIIG)
source.description: Federal Item Identification Guide (FIIG) Index is a search engine on the WWW listing all available FIIGs.  You can search by using the Index by Name Code, Index by Name or by entering the first three characters of the search item.  Selecting any FIIG will take you to the FIIG cover page. You may then choose to view the FIIG's contents or return to the index of available FIIGs
